			<script type="application/json" data-sveltekit-fetched data-url="/diagram/example/074J9y1o9BM/server">{"status":200,"statusText":"","headers":{},"body":"{\"diagram\":{\"id\":\"074J9y1o9BM\",\"name\":\"Conditional Statement Flowchart\",\"description\":\"A flowchart for a conditional statement visually represents decision-making in a program, using a diamond-shaped symbol to depict conditions that evaluate to \\\"True\\\" or \\\"False.\\\" It clearly shows the different paths the program takes based on whether the condition is satisfied or not, making it easier to trace logic. This type of flowchart simplifies understanding and debugging of if-else or switch-case constructs in programming.\",\"imageURL\":\"https://svg.template.creately.com/074J9y1o9BM\",\"thumbnailURL\":\"https://svg.template.creately.com/074J9y1o9BM\",\"owner\":\"Library Admin\",\"tags\":[\"flowchart\"],\"relatedDiagrams\":[{\"id\":\"KIzBBmUVo7w\",\"name\":\"AI Flowchart\",\"description\":\"Use this AI Flowchart example to efficiently build, validate, optimize, and deploy your machine learning model. The step-by-step process covered in this example provides everything from problem definition and data collection to model validation and hyperparameter tuning. Start streamlining your workflow and stay ahead of the curve with our AI Flowchart today.\",\"imageURL\":\"https://svg.template.creately.com/KIzBBmUVo7w\",\"thumbnailURL\":\"https://svg.template.creately.com/KIzBBmUVo7w\",\"owner\":\"Library Admin\",\"tags\":[\"flowchart\"],\"rating\":0,\"ratingCount\":0},{\"id\":\"i5pfs5d61\",\"name\":\"Pathophysiology Flowchart\",\"description\":\"A pathophysiology flowchart visually represents how a disease process unfolds from its initial cause to clinical manifestations. It often begins with an etiological factor, such as an infection or genetic mutation, and then outlines subsequent cellular, tissue, and organ-level changes. By detailing each step in this chain of events, the flowchart aids healthcare professionals and students in understanding disease mechanisms. It may also incorporate feedback loops to depict how specific factors can worsen or alleviate the condition. Ultimately, a pathophysiology flowchart helps clarify complex biological processes and supports better diagnostic and therapeutic decision-making.\",\"imageURL\":\"https://svg.template.creately.com/i5pfs5d61\",\"thumbnailURL\":\"https://svg.template.creately.com/i5pfs5d61\",\"owner\":\"Library Admin\",\"tags\":[\"flowchart\"],\"rating\":4.6,\"ratingCount\":8906},{\"id\":\"i0u3mxz62\",\"name\":\"Employee Flowchart\",\"description\":\"\\n\\nA Employee Flowchart is a useful tool to assist Human Resources (HR) departments. It provides a visual layout of the employee hierarchy within an organization. It outlines employee job roles, responsibilities, and reporting structures in a clear and straightforward manner. By using a flowchart, HR teams can quickly identify any potential issues regarding employee roles, expectations, and overall communication. It effectively highlights employee roles, allowing HR departments to effectively manage and improve organizational functions.\",\"imageURL\":\"https://svg.template.creately.com/i0u3mxz62\",\"thumbnailURL\":\"https://svg.template.creately.com/i0u3mxz62\",\"owner\":\"Library Admin\",\"tags\":[\"flowchart\"],\"rating\":0,\"ratingCount\":0},{\"id\":\"jgqc1q4r1\",\"name\":\"Nervous System Flowchart \",\"description\":\"Flowchart illustrating the human nervous system. Learn how the nerves and the cells carry messages to and from the brain with this nervous system flowchart.\",\"imageURL\":\"https://svg.template.creately.com/jgqc1q4r1\",\"thumbnailURL\":\"https://svg.template.creately.com/jgqc1q4r1\",\"owner\":\"Creately Templates\",\"tags\":[\"flowchart\",\" research\",\" education\"],\"rating\":0,\"ratingCount\":0},{\"id\":\"G58If1XC2yj\",\"name\":\"ATM Process Flowchart\",\"description\":\"An ATM Process Flowchart details the step-by-step interaction between a user and an ATM to complete a transaction, such as withdrawing cash. It begins with the user inserting their bank card, followed by the machine prompting for a PIN entry to verify identity. Once verified, the flowchart shows options for different transactions like cash withdrawal, balance inquiry, or deposit. If a cash withdrawal is selected, the flowchart proceeds to steps where the user enters an amount, the ATM checks the account balance, and dispenses cash if funds are sufficient. Finally, the transaction is completed, and the card is returned, with a receipt issued as the process ends. This flowchart visually clarifies each action, ensuring efficient and secure ATM operations for users and banks.\",\"imageURL\":\"https://svg.template.creately.com/G58If1XC2yj\",\"thumbnailURL\":\"https://svg.template.creately.com/G58If1XC2yj\",\"owner\":\"Library Admin\",\"tags\":[\"flowchart\"],\"rating\":0,\"ratingCount\":0},{\"id\":\"jhsnw9or1\",\"name\":\"Sample flowchart \",\"description\":\"Flowcharts are mostly used to show through shapes and images how a certain process is performed, in a chronological order, from start to finish. Use this editable simple flowchart to start visualizing. Explore more visual frameworks and templates on Creately+ Community Hub. \",\"imageURL\":\"https://svg.template.creately.com/jhsnw9or1\",\"thumbnailURL\":\"https://svg.template.creately.com/jhsnw9or1\",\"owner\":\"Creately Templates\",\"tags\":[\"flowchart\",\" diagrams\"],\"rating\":0,\"ratingCount\":0},{\"id\":\"hbsuu9311\",\"name\":\"If Then Flowchart\",\"description\":\"An \\\"If Then Flowchart\\\" is a visual tool used to represent conditional logic within a process or algorithm. It begins with a decision point that checks an \\\"if\\\" condition, directing the flow toward different outcomes based on whether the condition is met. Each branch in the flowchart represents a subsequent \\\"then\\\" action or alternative path, simplifying complex decision-making processes. This type of flowchart is commonly utilized in programming, business process modeling, and troubleshooting scenarios to illustrate clear, step-by-step conditional paths. Ultimately, it enhances clarity and efficiency by ensuring all potential outcomes are considered and documented in a structured format.\",\"imageURL\":\"https://svg.template.creately.com/hbsuu9311\",\"thumbnailURL\":\"https://svg.template.creately.com/hbsuu9311\",\"owner\":\"Library Admin\",\"tags\":[\"flowchart\"],\"rating\":4.9,\"ratingCount\":769},{\"id\":\"iun5p3qz\",\"name\":\"SMART Goals ( Flowchart)\\n\",\"description\":\"\\n\\nA SMART Goals Flowchart is a powerful tool for effective management. It is an acronym for Specific, Measurable, Achievable, Relevant, and Time-bound. Each step of the flowchart guides leaders through an organized system for setting and achieving goals. The end result is well-defined objectives that are actionable and on track for success. By breaking down complex tasks into individual steps, managers are able to develop clear strategies for their organization that increase efficiency and performance. With a SMART Goals Flowchart, teams have the necessary tools to make informed decisions and confidently keep their business goals on track.\",\"imageURL\":\"https://svg.template.creately.com/iun5p3qz\",\"thumbnailURL\":\"https://svg.template.creately.com/iun5p3qz\",\"owner\":\"Library Admin\",\"tags\":[\"flowchart\"],\"rating\":0,\"ratingCount\":0},{\"id\":\"zjUg2B9Olxa\",\"name\":\"Flowchart for Programming\",\"description\":\"A flowchart for programming represents the logical flow of a program, from the start to the end, including processes, decisions, loops, and data handling.\\nIt visually demonstrates how the program handles inputs, processes them, and outputs results, ensuring clarity and ease of understanding for developers.\\nThe flowchart is a useful tool for planning, debugging, and refining programs before writing the actual code.\",\"imageURL\":\"https://svg.template.creately.com/zjUg2B9Olxa\",\"thumbnailURL\":\"https://svg.template.creately.com/zjUg2B9Olxa\",\"owner\":\"Library Admin\",\"tags\":[\"flowchart\"],\"rating\":0,\"ratingCount\":0},{\"id\":\"dKXtbnXS9yq\",\"name\":\"Objections Flowchart Example\",\"description\":\"The Objections Flowchart Example is a visual representation that outlines a systematic approach for addressing and overcoming objections in a structured manner. This flowchart illustrates the step-by-step process of identifying common objections, categorizing them, and providing tailored responses or solutions for each objection type. By following this flowchart, teams can enhance their communication skills, anticipate challenges, and effectively navigate conversations, resulting in improved customer interactions, heightened problem-solving abilities, and ultimately, increased success in addressing objections. \",\"imageURL\":\"https://svg.template.creately.com/dKXtbnXS9yq\",\"thumbnailURL\":\"https://svg.template.creately.com/dKXtbnXS9yq\",\"owner\":\"Library Admin\",\"tags\":[\"flowchart\",\" diagrams\"],\"rating\":0,\"ratingCount\":0},{\"id\":\"V0kA5T3zsG1\",\"name\":\"Parallel Process Flowchart\",\"description\":\"A Parallel Process Flowchart represents multiple processes or tasks that occur simultaneously within a system. It begins with a common starting point, branching into separate paths that outline each parallel task or process. Each branch operates independently, showing steps or actions specific to that process while indicating that all tasks are executed concurrently. At the end of the parallel tasks, the flowchart typically reconverges, either to a single point or to complete the workflow. This type of flowchart is essential for visualizing workflows in systems where tasks can run at the same time, like in multi-threaded operations or project management with concurrent activities.\",\"imageURL\":\"https://svg.template.creately.com/V0kA5T3zsG1\",\"thumbnailURL\":\"https://svg.template.creately.com/V0kA5T3zsG1\",\"owner\":\"Library Admin\",\"tags\":[\"flowchart\"],\"rating\":0,\"ratingCount\":0},{\"id\":\"jhkacrab1\",\"name\":\"Protein Synthesis Flowchart \",\"description\":\"\\n\\nThis protein synthesis flowchart is a great tool for any student learning about protein synthesis. It offers an easy-to-understand visual representation of the process of protein synthesis. From the initial transcription of a gene to the final product of a protein, this flowchart makes it simple for students to learn about protein synthesis. Moreover, this flowchart encourages students to trace the individual steps involved in the creation of a protein, making it an effective way for them to comprehend the complexity of protein synthesis. All in all, this tool can be a great resource for students of all levels learning about biology and biochemistry.\",\"imageURL\":\"https://svg.template.creately.com/jhkacrab1\",\"thumbnailURL\":\"https://svg.template.creately.com/jhkacrab1\",\"owner\":\"Library Admin\",\"tags\":[\"flowchart\"],\"rating\":0,\"ratingCount\":0},{\"id\":\"074J9y1o9BM\",\"name\":\"Conditional Statement Flowchart\",\"description\":\"A flowchart for a conditional statement visually represents decision-making in a program, using a diamond-shaped symbol to depict conditions that evaluate to \\\"True\\\" or \\\"False.\\\" It clearly shows the different paths the program takes based on whether the condition is satisfied or not, making it easier to trace logic. This type of flowchart simplifies understanding and debugging of if-else or switch-case constructs in programming.\",\"imageURL\":\"https://svg.template.creately.com/074J9y1o9BM\",\"thumbnailURL\":\"https://svg.template.creately.com/074J9y1o9BM\",\"owner\":\"Library Admin\",\"tags\":[\"flowchart\"],\"rating\":0,\"ratingCount\":0},{\"id\":\"jrsrv16a3\",\"name\":\"Meeting Flowchart Template \",\"description\":\"Flowchart template to map, improve, design and analyze processes during meetings. Use this editable template to customize it to your own needs. Explore more visual frameworks and templates on Creately+ Community Hub.\",\"imageURL\":\"https://svg.template.creately.com/jrsrv16a3\",\"thumbnailURL\":\"https://svg.template.creately.com/jrsrv16a3\",\"owner\":\"Creately Templates\",\"tags\":[\"flowchart\",\"flowchart template\"],\"rating\":0,\"ratingCount\":0},{\"id\":\"jny57xed8\",\"name\":\"Horizontal Flowchart Template\",\"description\":\"Editable horizontal flowchart template to illustrate process steps. Use Creately to create flowcharts to visualize your processes, systems, and information flows. Explore more visual frameworks and templates on Creately+ Community Hub.\",\"imageURL\":\"https://svg.template.creately.com/jny57xed8\",\"thumbnailURL\":\"https://svg.template.creately.com/jny57xed8\",\"owner\":\"Library Admin\",\"tags\":[\"flowchart\",\"horizontal flowchart\",\"process\",\"process mapping\"],\"rating\":0,\"ratingCount\":0},{\"id\":\"iutwrw2j1\",\"name\":\"Chatbot Flowchart\",\"description\":\"A Chatbot Flowchart is a visual representation of a chatbot’s conversational logic and decision-making process. It maps out user inputs, chatbot responses, and potential pathways, ensuring smooth and efficient interactions. Key elements include user queries, bot responses, decision points, and fallback options for handling errors or unclear inputs. Businesses use chatbot flowcharts to design seamless customer service, lead generation, and automated support experiences. This structured diagram helps developers and teams refine chatbot workflows for improved efficiency and user satisfaction.\",\"imageURL\":\"https://svg.template.creately.com/iutwrw2j1\",\"thumbnailURL\":\"https://svg.template.creately.com/iutwrw2j1\",\"owner\":\"Library Admin\",\"tags\":[\"flowchart\"],\"rating\":0,\"ratingCount\":0}],\"translations\":{},\"langCode\":\"en\"}}"}</script>
